r with us more often than at your mom\'s and our waiters know exactly how many spoons of sugar do you prefer in your tea, you have all the chances to become a member of our club. Our manager will give you a form to fill in and will give you the Odessa-mama card, which will allow you to get special treats. We don\'t want to disappoint you but this is not a discount, this is a sign of our favour.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; *Odessa-mama card holders can get special treats every day:</p><br />\r\n- by Mondays – half-a-litre of homemade alcohol drink: khrenovukha, honey drink with pepper, garlic or currant drink,<br />\r\n- by Tuesdays you can eat vareniki,<br /> \r\n- by Wednesdays – order any soup for free,<br />\r\n- by Thursdays try any dish made by a Jewish mom,<br />\r\n- by Fridays you can drink 1 litre of uzvar or homemade fruit drink, <br />\r\n- by Saturdays to cheer you up we treat you with drunken kvass – one litre. <br />\r\n- by Sundays – any desert is for free.<br /><br />\r\n*This offer is valid on weekdays after 4 PM and through the whole day on weekends. You can\'t order a treat take-away. Beside ordering the treat we ask our guests to order something from the menu.<br />\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; We\'ll invite you for our celebrations and parties; you\'ll be the first one to know about our offers and new dishes on the menu. Don\'t forget to check your mail!<br />\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Odessa-mama cardholders who have birthday will get free and unlimited homemade alcohol drinks nastoyka!<br />\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Those of you who come often to spend special occasions with us or just have a good time, we can treat you with something really special: nastoyka bottle or fruits, a cake or a striped vest. <br />\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Take int